title: RN Upgrade: Resolve duplicate symbol issue
body:
### User Story

As a developer, I want to make RN upgrade build work so we can move forward with planned changes.

### Description

*Type*: Bug

*Summary*: Fix build, or at least move fail one step further.

#### Expected behavior
Fail better.

#### Actual behavior
Fail 600+ times.

### Reproduction
Devs only: build the things

### Solution
Don't know. See https://stackoverflow.com/questions/24298144/duplicate-symbols-for-architecture-x86-64-under-xcode for hints (tried common blocks but didn't work).

### Additional Information
* Operating System: iOS
